name: 3-D Animation and Game Design - BFA
university: University of the Incarnate Word, USA
overview: You will cover everything from business planning, soil analysis, livestock production and welfare and crop production to environmental protection. In addition to essential theory, you will benefit from hands-on experience in laboratories and on farms and via agricultural case studies.
requirement: UG IELTS 6.0 (no band less than 5.5) PG IELTS (Taught MSc and MBA) - 6.5 (no band less than 5.5) PG IETLS (Research MScR and PhD) - 6.5 (writing 6.0 and no other band less than 5.5)
